snippet.title: Gatewalkers - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1125710/Gatewalkers/?utm_source=youtube&campaign=gameplay_trailer&content=1

Gatewalkers is a cooperative action RPG game with survival elements, where players travel across different worlds in order to save their own. Explore procedurally generated worlds, face hostile inhabitants, face challenges like extreme weather conditions, toxic atmosphere, lack of water and more.

WWW: https://gatewalkers.com
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/gatewalkersgame
Twitter: https://twitter.com/gatewalkersgame
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/gatewalkersgame/
Discord: https://discord.gg/8Tn76pT
